data.description: Welcome to this charming one bedroom, one bath condo! Nestled in a peaceful community, this home offers a cozy living space with a well-appointed galley kitchen, perfect for whipping up your favorite meals. The bedroom is spacious and inviting, ideal for relaxation after a long day. Along with ample closet space. With easy access to nearby shops and restaurants, this condo is the perfect place to be your home!
